Class SimpleTileRectangle

  • Object

      • com.xilinx.rapidwright.design.SimpleTileRectangle

  • public class SimpleTileRectangle
extends TileRectangle
    A TileRectangle that uses Row/Column indices for storage. Fast, but not relocatable.

      • extendToCorresponding

        public void extendToCorresponding(RelocatableTileRectangle rect,
                                  Site currentAnchor,
                                  SiteInst templateAnchor)
        Extend the Rectangle so that a shifted rectangle is inside. The Rectangle is assumed to be located relative to some anchor. The anchor is shifted from templateAnchor to currentAnchor. This location relative to the new anchor is then included in the Rectangle.
        Specified by:
